CMD: sudo apt update = to update to the freshes packet list
sudo apt upgrade (-y) this allows upgrades within the current Linux version without prompts
How to create a low level user: sudo su - & then usermod -aG (name of user) & chsh -s /bin/bash (name of user) to add new user with sudo privileges & then grep 'sudo' /etc/group
Multiplexer is a quality of life feature, not currently installed.
